  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Assesing the impact of mentoring on the lifestyle choices of adolescents who are overweight
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Randomized controlled trial of the impact of weekly contacts with mentors to improve physical
      activity pattern, self esteem, and weight loss in obese teenagers over a 6 month period.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
